{"tid":1076262,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男人分手時點解可以咁絕情？","createTime":"2019-03-24T17:06:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T14:33:37.000Z","uid":88967,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"554be8a145f4f75b8c13e7cb31b9a64178536ad8","tid":1076262,"uid":88967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T17:06:15.000Z","msg":"最近男朋友同我講分手，話覺得我地唔合適，同我一齊變得有壓力。我地本身識咗唔耐就一齊，一齊咗都不過三個月以內既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我本身真係諗爆頭都諗唔明，我地都唔係拍得耐，遇到問題唔係應該試下磨合先嫁咩？唔試下又點知唔得？我咁樣同佢講完後，佢同我講反而更覺得我同佢係兩個思路既人，佢好理性而我好理想主義。<br />\n<br />\n由拍拖到宜家，我地從來都冇鬧過交。我已經盡力去體貼佢、對佢好、遷就佢。佢好忙，我地一星期先見得一晚。佢話最近呢半個月都唔見，我都冇lur過要見，亦冇要求其他嘢(eg傾電話)。但我覺得如果有心的話，其實一日內send一兩個msg俾對方，表示有將對方放響心上，都唔係好花時間既事(？)反正呢半個月以黎，我地每日都好少msg，有都多數係我主動send俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似俾人放置咗咁。<br />\n<br />\n本身以為係我自己會頂唔順講分手先，點知竟然被分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實係咪根本佢對我唔夠鍾意，所以分手時搵個藉口咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？男人講分手的話，復合既可能性係咪好低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\np.s.借人ac<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"194b0ba223ce74840b73fd7092ba96eb67b2c216","tid":1076262,"uid":27416,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T17:07:46.000Z","msg":"絕唔絕情係睇下個to do list 清晒未啫"},{"pid":"620834e3b06a6ef7410ba65c6664f2fbdb0c8d0f","tid":1076262,"uid":88967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"194b0ba223ce74840b73fd7092ba96eb67b2c216","tid":1076262,"uid":27416,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T17:07:46.000Z","msg":"絕唔絕情係睇下個to do list 清晒未啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T17:08:07.000Z","msg":"即係咩意思？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc123d3f5e1e21aa5da260d742ce5e966189f2b2","tid":1076262,"uid":18547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T17:08:42.000Z","msg":"可能忍左好耐"},{"pid":"827eab1f6b5f638db2ae9161ec404c35c91f3bf6","tid":1076262,"uid":88967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc123d3f5e1e21aa5da260d742ce5e966189f2b2","tid":1076262,"uid":18547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T17:08:42.000Z","msg":"可能忍左好耐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T17:10:29.000Z","msg":"但我自問好遷就佢，一次脾氣都冇發過，對佢完全係千依百順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 身邊d朋友話我愛得好委屈"},{"pid":"3035db05db2187777d3886aca0744c8642c9a9af","tid":1076262,"uid":49979,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T17:14:03.000Z","msg":"人既問題 唔關男女事"},{"pid":"32f076a3954ac941b6501199d143c2b77385bd38","tid":1076262,"uid":16956,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T17:14:28.000Z","msg":"有其他女 搵籍口姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29a71387512ae2c240719ef6dfd465b9427dfa2a","tid":1076262,"uid":18547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"827eab1f6b5f638db2ae9161ec404c35c91f3bf6","tid":1076262,"uid":88967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc123d3f5e1e21aa5da260d742ce5e966189f2b2","tid":1076262,"uid":18547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T17:08:42.000Z","msg":"可能忍左好耐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T17:10:29.000Z","msg":"但我自問好遷就佢，一次脾氣都冇發過，對佢完全係千依百順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 身邊d朋友話我愛得好委屈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T17:17:30.000Z","msg":"有d人就你咁撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nI know"},{"pid":"e035be1ed1bb117775319d8313cf3b3f8ff201be","tid":1076262,"uid":88967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32f076a3954ac941b6501199d143c2b77385bd38","tid":1076262,"uid":169